    "created_at": "2016-09-07T10:17:05Z",
    "updated_at": "2016-09-07T10:17:05Z",
    "body": "There is an API for it. For applications with real time continual processes (audio, timers, responding to external messages like MIDI / OSC) it is needed.\n\nSee: https://github.com/supercollider/supercollider/blob/2744239f2252eebb2d952b7aa56134d53ce243ea/common/SC_Apple.mm\n\nI think its this:\n\n```\nunint64_t options = (NSActivityUserInitiated | NSActivityIdleSystemSleepDisabled) | NSActivityLatencyCritical;\n\nid activity = [[NSProcessInfo processInfo] beginActivityWithOptions: options reason:@\"avoiding audio hiccups and reducing latency\"];\n```\n\nhttp://stackoverflow.com/questions/19847293/disable-app-nap-in-macos-10-9-mavericks-application\n"
  },
